title: Blazin' 5

description:
The Blazing 5 is back and Colin talks with RJ Bell of Pregame.com and Fox Sports Radio about his picks and whether the Wise Guys in Vegas agree or disagree.  Plus, Colin reveals a bonus pick not in his Blazing 5 in this exclusive podcast.
